     H            Y.                                                      EER030
     F** ALDRZ7 **************************************
     F*DELETE SIGN-ON INFORMATION FOR HANDY        *
     F*       T.SAKAKI         2015.10.15            *
     F************************************************
     FALDPLZ5 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   60WTHMS
     I                                        7  140WDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C*
     C           K#WSI     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@WSID 10
     C*
     C                     MOVELW#WSID    K@WSID
     C*
     C                     SETOF                     98
     C           K#WSI     SETGTALDPLZ51
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           K#WSI     REDPEALDPLZ51                 98
     C   98                LEAVE
     C           A@SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL'D'       A@SKJY
     C                     Z-ADDWDATE     A@OFDT
     C                     Z-ADDWTHMS     A@OFTM
     C                     UPDATALDPLZ51
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * END                                                *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
